Comment: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,TYPE 3 FOLHA 2
Comment: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:56.17,Main,,0,0,0,,TYPE 4 FOLHA 3 {PUTA QUE PARIU}
Comment: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,TYPE CELULAR 2
